sourcesContent: import config from '../../config.json' function ViewMembersTableItem ({item}) { console.log("item", item) let data = { name: item.member.firstName + " " + item.member.lastName, batch: item.member.batch, position: item.member.position, url: item.member.transaction.image.url, } return {item.member.firstName+" "+item.member.lastName} {item.member.batch} {item.member.position} {item.transaction} } export default ViewMembersTableItem
